  <h2>Donate online</h2>
  


  <p>DrugScience is the only completely independent, science-led drugs charity. We aim to provide clear, evidence based information on drugs without interference from political or commercial interest. Read more about us and our impact. Our work relies on funding from members of the public. Your donation will help us to continue our work. <br/><br/><strong>JustGiving</strong><br/>We encourage you to donate a small amount each month via direct debit using the Just Giving option below (using the Monthly Donation option). This option will allow Just Giving to claim GiftAid on your donation. <br/><br/>We are also happy to receive one off donations via JustGiving, which will still allow to collect GiftAid.</p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://www.justgiving.com/hxlnzllkyk/donate/?utm_source=website_cid34915&amp;utm_medium=buttons&amp;utm_content=hxlnzllkyk&amp;utm_campaign=donate_dd_purple"><img alt="Set up a direct debit with JustGiving" src="http://www.justgiving.com/charities/content/images/logo-buttons/purple/donate_dd_purple.gif"/></a></p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://www.justgiving.com/hxlnzllkyk/raisemoney/?utm_source=website_cid34915&amp;utm_medium=buttons&amp;utm_content=hxlnzllkyk&amp;utm_campaign=makeapage_your_white"><img alt="Make your page with JustGiving" src="http://www.justgiving.com/charities/content/images/logo-buttons/white/makeapage_your_white.gif"/></a></p>
<p> </p>
